body_html: @taion I am finally back to doing a write up and I hope to send it this week but I suspect that means next week. Also I confirmed what you saw. Regardless of version, even the latest head of master, you need WINOGRAD on for the boost. I am sure we have an internal bug to make that on by default or on when it makes sense, but I am going to start obnoxiously asking about it.
